(January 27, 1955.)

(Republished.)

In the Matter of the Election of Directors and Officers of National Kiddie Rides, Inc. Charles Katz et al., Appellants; Fred Rafanello et al., Respondents.

Order of July 31, 1953, unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the respondents, and the appeal from order entered August 25, 1953, denying reargument, is dismissed. No opinion. Present — Peck, P. J., Callahan, Breitel, Bastow and Botein, JJ. [See ante, p. 804.]
